HEADER  FIXEDWOO linkule test — WS with potential pinned at fixed point
$ Tests the FIXEDWOO potential-form linkule. The potential is a WS shape
$ scaled so V(R=PARAM1) = TVR (the V keyword).
CHANNEL  16O + 48CA
ELAB = 56
realpotential FIXEDWOO
V = 1.0  R = 4.5  A = 0.6  REALPOWE = 1.0  PARAM1 = 3.0
W = 5  RI0 = 1.27  AI = .5  RC0 = 1.2
ELASTIC SCATTERING
;
end
